>>> #Find the simple interest on Rs 200 for 5 years at 5% per year
>>> #Taking the variables
>>> p=200
>>> r=5
>>> t=5
>>> i=(p*r*t)/100
>>> print("The interest is:",i)
The interest is: 50.0
